  <item rdf:about="2022/0423-kamakura/">
            <title>2022/04/23: 鎌倉ハイキング</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2022/0423-kamakura/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>モンベルのシューズを買った娘さんと張り切って出かける。</p>

<p>巣作りシーズンなのか、カラスの縄張り争いがやかましい。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6932.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6932.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6932.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6932.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6932"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdimg_6931.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdimg_6931.jpg" height="96" alt="hdimg_6931" /></a></p>

<p>筍もめっちゃ生えてる。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6933.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6933.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6933.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6933.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6933"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6936.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6936.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6936.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6936.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6936"/></a></p>

<p>ビールの美味しい季節になりました。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6937.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6937.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6937.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6937.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6937"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6941.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6941.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6941.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6941.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6941"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6942.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6942.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6942.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6942.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6942"/></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2022-2022-04T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
