  <item rdf:about="2022/0325-dinner/">
            <title>2022/03/25: 野毛</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2022/0325-dinner/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>伝説のOB達とエンドレスで飲む。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://tabelog.com/kanagawa/A1401/A140102/14004194/">第一亭</a>
神奈川県横浜市中区日ノ出町1-20
045-231-6137
</pre>

<p>久しぶりにパタンを食べた。
しじみの醤油漬けは、ユッケと同じで禁止されたので、かなり昔からやめたそうです。残念。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6880.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6880.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6880.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6880.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6880"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6882.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6882.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6882.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6882.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6882"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6883.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6883.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6883.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6883.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6883"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6884.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6884.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6884.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6884.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6884"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6887.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6887.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6887.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6887.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6887"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6888.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6888.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6888.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6888.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6888"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6889.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6889.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6889.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6889.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6889"/></a></p>

<p>2軒目。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://tabelog.com/kanagawa/A1401/A140104/14000049/">野毛おでん</a>
神奈川県横浜市中区吉田町2-6
045-251-3234
</pre>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6890.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6890.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6890.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6890.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6890"/></a></p>

<p>3軒目。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://tabelog.com/kanagawa/A1401/A140102/14014987/">Piano Bar Lyon</a>
神奈川県横浜市中区野毛町2-94
045-262-3110
</pre>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6895.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6895.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6895.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6895.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6895"/></a></p>

<p>4軒目はカラオケボックスで始発まで滞在して解散。</p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2022-2022-03T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
