  <item rdf:about="2022/0320-yokosuka/">
            <title>2022/03/20: 横須賀</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2022/0320-yokosuka/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>娘がネットで見つけた<a href="https://bandainamco-am.co.jp/others/tondemi/yokosuka/">トンデミ</a>へ行ってみる。バンナム経営なのね。</p>

<p>トランポリン。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6860.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6860.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6860.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6860.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6860"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdimg_6861.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdimg_6861.jpg" height="96" alt="hdimg_6861" /></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdimg_6862.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdimg_6862.jpg" height="96" alt="hdimg_6862" /></a></p>

<p>ダンクシュート。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdtrimg_6864.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdtrimg_6864.jpg" height="96" alt="hdtrimg_6864" /></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdtrimg_6865.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdtrimg_6865.jpg" height="96" alt="hdtrimg_6865" /></a></p>

<p>クライミング。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdtrimg_6870.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdtrimg_6870.jpg" height="96" alt="hdtrimg_6870" /></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/hdtrimg_6871.mp4" class="video swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/video/96/hdtrimg_6871.jpg" height="96" alt="hdtrimg_6871" /></a></p>

<p>ロープウォーク狭いのでめっちゃしんどい。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6866.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6866.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6866.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6866.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6866"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6869.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6869.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6869.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6869.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6869"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_6872.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6872.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_6872.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_6872.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_6872"/></a></p>

<p>90分でヘロヘロになった。子供向けかと思ってなめてました。めっちゃしんどい。</p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2022-2022-03T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
